"async/go-loop" is a function that takes a channel and a function
that takes a channel and returns a function.

The function passed to async/go-loop will be called with a channel
that will be used to send messages to the function passed to
async/go-loop.

The function passed to async/go-loop will be called repeatedly
with a channel that will be used to send messages to the function
passed to async/go-loop.

